0communication%20with%20Mr%20Simha's%20personal%20assistant%20(PA)%20and%20office%20regarding%20the%20visitor's%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20that%20he%20possessed%20no%20additional%20information%20beyond%20what%20he%20had%20already%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D%20jumped%20from%20the%20visitor's%20gallery%20to%20the%20House%20yesterday.%20They%20managed%20to%20release%20yellow%20smoke%20from%20aerosol%20canisters%20before%20they%20were%20caught%20by%20some%20of%20the%20parliamentarians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20those%20two%20were%20causing%20panic%20inside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20two%20other%20protesters%20-%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20-%20were%20caught%20releasing%20coloured%20smoke%20on%20a%20road%20outside%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20questioning%2C%20the%20four%20accused%20told%20cops%20that%20they%20were%20concerned%20about%20issues%20like%20unemployment%20and%20Manipur%20violence.%20They%20said%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20catch%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20parliamentarians%20and%20start%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20shock%20at%20the%20breach%2C%20several%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20said%20visitors%20have%20to%20clear%20five%20levels%20of%20security%20before%20entering%20the%20complex%20and%20that%20signatures%20from%20the%20office%20of%20an%20MP%20are%20needed%20for%20a%20pass%20to%20the%20visitors'%20gallery.%20The%20breach%20took%20place%2022%20years%20after%20the%20attack%20on%20Parliament%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20has%20trained%20their%20guns%20on%20Mr%20Simha%20and%20is%20claiming%20that%20a%20thorough%20security%20check%20wasn't%20done%20by%20the%20MP%20before%20issuing%20the%20passes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPratap%20Simha%20won%20from%20the%20Mysore%20constituency%20with%2043.46%25%20of%20votes%20in%202014%20and%20increased%20his%20vote%20share%20to%2052.27%25%20in%20the%202019%20elections.%20The%2042-year-old%20is%20a%20former%20journalist%20and%20is%20well-known%20for%20a%20series%20of%20columns.%20He%20also%20wrote%20a%20biography%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20a%20farmer%2C%20the%20MP%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20he%20idolises%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702533900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F21h0a8e8_pratap-simha_625x300_14_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-security-breach-pratap-simha-bjp-mp-explains-why-his-office-issued-passes-to-parliament-breach-accused-4671343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%2C%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20providing%20Parliament%20passes%20to%20the%20two%20accused%20responsible%20for%20causing%20chaos%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20gas%20canisters%2C%20met%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20offered%20an%20explanation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-security-breach-pratap-simha-bjp-mp-explains-why-his-office-issued-passes-to-parliament-breach-accused-4671343%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-security-breach-pratap-simha-bjp-mp-explains-why-his-office-issued-passes-to-parliament-breach-accused-4671343%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-security-breach-pratap-simha-bjp-mp-explains-why-his-office-issued-passes-to-parliament-breach-accused-4671343%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranbir%20revealed%20THIS%20about%20Raj%20Kapoor's%20fandom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702533881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105980604%2Cimgsize-51300.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.c