%20healthier%2C%20in%20my%20lifetime%2C%20feels%20like%20relief%2C%20like%20redemption%2C%20like%20a%20gift%2C%20and%20not%20something%20to%20hide%20behind%20and%20once%20again%20be%20ridiculed%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20global%20influencer%20revealed%20that%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20her%20weight-loss%20journey%20was%20knee%20surgery%20in%202021%20after%20which%20she%20started%20to%20make%20stricter%20efforts%20to%20maintain%20a%20healthier%20lifestyle.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20knee%20surgery%2C%20I%20started%20hiking%20and%20setting%20new%20distance%20goals%20each%20week.%20I%20could%20eventually%20hike%20three%20to%20five%20miles%20every%20day%20and%20a%2010-mile%20straight-up%20hike%20on%20weekends%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20stronger%2C%20more%20fit%20and%20more%20alive%20than%20I'd%20felt%20in%20years%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20eat%20my%20last%20meal%20at%204%20o'clock%2C%20drink%20a%20gallon%20of%20water%20a%20day%2C%20and%20use%20the%20WeightWatchers%20principles%20of%20counting%20points.%20I%20had%20an%20awareness%20of%20(weight-loss)%20medications%20but%20felt%20I%20had%20to%20prove%20I%20had%20the%20willpower%20to%20do%20it.%20I%20now%20no%20longer%20feel%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20talk%20show%20host%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Findian-american-medical-student-rijul-maini-crowned-miss-india-usa-2023-4667054%5C%22%3EIndian-American%20Medical%20Student%20Rijul%20Maini%20Crowned%20Miss%20India%20USA%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Winfrey%20did%20not%20reveal%20the%20drug%20she%20takes%2C%20she%20said%20that%20her%20approach%20to%20using%20pharmaceutical%20aids%20came%20in%20July%20during%20a%20taped%20panel%20conversation%20with%20weight%20loss%20experts%20and%20clinicians.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20the%20biggest%20aha%20along%20with%20many%20people%20in%20that%20audience%2C%26quot%3B%20Winfrey%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20had%20been%20blaming%20herself%20for%20being%20overweight%20without%20realising%20that%20she%20had%20a%20predisposition%20%26quot%3Bthat%20no%20amount%20of%20willpower%20is%20going%20to%20control%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20said%20that%20her%20weight%20loss%20and%20fitness%20progress%20have%20allowed%20her%20to%20lead%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20vital%20and%20vibrant%20life%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Hawaii%2C%20I%20live%20on%20a%20mountain%2C%20and%20there's%20this%20big%20hill%20-%20I%20used%20to%20look%20out%20the%20window%20every%20morning%20and%20say%2C%20'God%2C%20one%20day%20I%20want%20to%20walk%20up%20that%20mountain.'%20Last%20year%20over%20Christmas%20I%20did%20it...It%20felt%20like%20redemption%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Winfrey's%20revelation%20comes%20amid%20a%20time%20when%20there%20has%20been%20a%20buzz%20around%20weight-loss%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy.%20The%20medication%20reportedly%20regulates%20hunger%20signals%20and%20allows%20people%20to%20feel%20full%20while%20eating%20less.%20However%2C%20experts%20have%20noted%20that%20the%20drug%20also%20has%20side%20effects%20such%20as%20nausea%2C%20diarrhoea%20and%20constipation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702533780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fs28gvumo_oprah-winfrey_625x300_14_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdone-with-shaming-oprah-winfrey-admits-to-using-weight-loss-medication-4671336%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Celebrity%20talk%20show%20host%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20recently%20revealed%20that%20she%20takes%20weight-loss%20medication%20to%20help%20manage%20her%20weight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdone-with-shaming-oprah-winfrey-admits-to-using-weight-loss-medication-4671336%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdone-with-shaming-oprah-winfrey-admits-to-using-weight-loss-medication-4671336%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdone-with-shaming-oprah-winfrey-admits-to-using-weight-loss-medication-4671336%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%204%20Theories%20To%20Explain%20BJP's%20State%20Shockers%20-%20Take%20Your%20Pick%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFour%20theories%20are%20in%20circulation%20in%20journalistic%20circles%20and%20also%20in%20the%20power%20corridors%20on%20why%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20oblige%20its%20big%20leaders%20while%20choosing%20chief%20ministers.%20Virtually%20unknown%20leaders%20have%20been%20given%20the%20responsibility%20to%20run%20three%20states%20-%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20after%20the%20BJP's%20historic%20wins%20in%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheory%201%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%20and%20Raman%20Singh%20being%20replaced%20by%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%20and%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20is%20an%20exercise%20in%20inter-generational%20shift.%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20has%20ruled%20the%20state%20for%20almost%20two%20decades.%20Similarly%2C%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%20and%20Raman%20Singh%20were%20the%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20the%20same%20time%20period.%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20is%20relatively%20younger%20but%20it's%20time%20to%20groom%20new%20leaders.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20this%20generational%20change%20is%20good%20for%20the%20health%20of%20the%20party.%20For%20the%20party%20to%20grow%2C%20new%20ideas%20and%20a%20fresh%20approach%20is%20needed%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20fast-changing%20society%2C%20otherwise%20the%20party%20will%20pay%20dearly.%20It%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20political%20career%20of%20these%20big%20leaders%20is%20over.%20The%20party%20will%20use%20their%20services%20at%20other%20levels%3B%20much%20bigger%20roles%20may%20be%20given%20to%20them%20as%20the%20party%20has%20exponentially%20grown%20since%202014%20and%20it%20needs%20leaders%20with%20vast%20experience%20to%20not%20only%20consolidate%20gains%20at%20the%20national%20level%20but%20also%20to%20create%20strategy%20for%20the%20party's%20future%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20theory%20advocates%20that%20the%20party%20should%20continuously%20cultivate%20new%20leaders%2C%20provide%20them%20new%20opportunities%20and%20utilise%20their%20talents.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20after%20becoming%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20given%20a%20glimpse%20of%20this%20thought%20process%20when%20a%20Margdarshak%20Mandal%20was%20created%20and%20top%20leaders%20like%20LK%20Advani%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20and%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20who%20had%20worked%20for%20the%20party%20for%20more%20than%20five%20decades%2C%20were%20consigned%20to%20it.%20The%20Mandal%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20consultative%20body%20which%2C%20if%20required%2C%20would%20provide%20inputs%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20party%20and%20the%20government.%20It%20later%20became%20clear%20that%20it%20was%20basically%20a%20VRS%20scheme%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20dominant%20leaders%20and%20clear%20the%20path%20for%20the%20new%20leadership%20of%20the%20party.%20Nobody%20knows%20if%20a%20similar%20plan%20is%20in%20store%20for%20Shivraj%2C%20Vasundhara%20and%20Raman%20Singh.%20It%20is%20still%20uncertain%20whether%20the%20replacements%20will%20be%20as%20good%20as%20their%20predecessors%20-%20not%20much%20is%20known%20about%20them%20and%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20that%20none%20of%20them%20have%20shown%20great%20promise%20or%20were%20in%20any%20way%20exceptional%20in%20their%20previous%20roles.%20But%20then%20the%20same%20was%20said%20for%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20and%20Bhupendra%20Patel.%20They%20were%20first-time%20MLAs.%20Under%20Dhami's%20leadership%2C%20the%20party%20won%20Uttarakhand%20and%20in%20Gujarat%20the%20BJP%20broke%20all%20records%20in%20electoral%20politics.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20pass%20judgement%20upon%20these%20three.%20But%20if%20this%20is%20part%20of%20a%20generational%20shift%20then%20many%20leaders%20at%20the%20national%20level%20and%20in%20states%20will%20be%20replaced%20sooner%20than%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20age%20cut-off%20and%20generational%20change%20concept%20will%20reach%20the%20very%20top%20or%20will%20an%20exception%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheory%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20done%20this%20to%20arrest%20the%20disease%20of%20cultism.%20It%20has%20been%20said%20in%20hushed%20tones%20that%20the%20party%20has%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20benefited%20tremendously%20from%20the%20personality%20cult%20of%20Modi%2C%20but%20there%20is%20serious%20thinking%20in%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20that%20the%20politics%20of%20personality%20cult%20will%20prove%20to%20be%20injurious%20to%20the%20party's%20health%2C%20like%20it%20was%20for%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Once%20a%20behemoth%20that%20would%20have%20been%20difficult%20to%20replace%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20suffered%20a%20spectacular%20downfall%20and%20is%20fighting%20to%20exist%2C%20irreparably%20wounded%20by%20the%20personality%20cult%20around%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20overcentralisation%20of%20power.%20Because%20a%20personality%20cult%20invariably%20leads%20to%20weakening%20of%20the%20organisation%20and%20overcentralisation%20of%20power.%20The%20leader%20becomes%20bigger%20than%20the%20party%20and%20institutions%20and%20structures%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20surrender%20to%20the%20cult%20due%20to%20over-dependence%20on%20the%20leader%20to%20win%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Modi%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20was%20a%20tall%20leader%20but%20under%20him%20the%20party%20had%20a%20semblance%20of%20collective%20leadership.%20Under%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20surrendered%20to%20his%20towering%20persona.%20The%20Modi%20cult%20has%20afflicted%20the%20party%20so%20deeply%20that%20veterans%20like%20Venkaiya%20Naidu%20have%20publicly%20called%20him%20a%20man%20with%20divine%20virtues.%20If%20there%20was%20one%20Devkant%20Barua%20in%20Congress%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20Indira%20and%20Indira%20is%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20there%20are%20many%20Devkant%20Baruas%20in%20the%20BJP%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20faced%20the%20personality%20cult%20in%20states.%20Kalyan%20Singh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20BS%20Yediyurappa%20in%20Karnataka%20were%20tall%20leaders%20in%20their%20own%20right%2C%20and%20if%20the%20party%20gained%20from%20them%2C%20it%20suffered%20as%20well.%20In%20UP%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20BJP%20lost%20elections%20because%20of%20their%20anger.%20Even%20this%20time%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20party%20had%20to%20face%20many%20uncomfortable%20moments%20due%20to%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia.%20Even%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20has%20dropped%20enough%20hints%20that%20he%20is%20not%20happy%20about%20the%20way%20he%20has%20been%20replaced%20and%20that%20party%20has%20to%20tread%20cautiously%20going%20forward.%20What%20is%20the%20guarantee%20that%20Vasundhara%20and%20Shivraj%20will%20not%20follow%20the%20path%20of%20Kalyan%20Singh%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%20and%20Yediyurappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheory%203%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20widely%20speculated%20that%20entire%20exercise%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20neutralise%20the%20Mandal%20politics%20and%20caste%20calculus%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20others%20in%20the%20opposition%20have%20been%20demanding%20that%20the%20Modi%20Government%20carry%20out%20a%20caste%20census%20like%20Nitish%20Kumar%20did%20in%20Bihar%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20uncomfortable%20with%20this.%20Because%20of%20ideological%20reasons%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20mentor%20RSS%20are%20hesitant%20to%20take%20a%20clear%20position%20on%20this%20issue.%20When%20Nitish%20Kumar%20made%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20report%20public%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20described%20caste%20politics%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsin%20that%20will%20be%20dangerous%20to%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%20But%20the%20BJP%20also%20knew%20that%20it%20would%20be%20dangerous%20to%20ignore%20OBC%20politics%20and%20it%20might%20damage%20the%20party.%20The%20appointment%20of%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20an%20OBC%20leader%2C%20and%20Vishnu%20Dev%20Sai%2C%20an%20adivasi%2C%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20this%20perspective%20too.%20Just%20one%20point.%20Shivraj%20is%20also%20an%20OBC%20leader%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20leaders%20in%20the%20country.%20Mohan%20Yadav%20is%20no%20match%20for%20Shivraj.%20To%20assume%20that%20appointing%20a%20leader%20from%20a%20particular%20caste%20or%20community%20will%20guarantee%20the%20votes%20of%20that%20community%20or%20caste%20is%20to%20assume%20too%20much.%20It%20does%20not%20happen%20unless%20the%20caste%20leader%20is%20charismatic%20and%20has%20a%20mass%20base.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20Vishnu%20Deo.%20Their%20appointment%20is%20good%20for%20optics%20but%20how%20much%20it%20will%20deliver%20has%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheory%204%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20known%20for%20excessive%20centralisation%20of%20power.%20Nothing%20moves%20without%20his%20consent%2C%20neither%20in%20the%20party%2C%20nor%20in%20the%20government.%20Ministers%20have%20no%20autonomy.%20This%20style%20of%20leadership%20has%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20the%20phenomenal%20expansion%20of%20the%20party.%20From%20two%20MPs%20in%201984%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20win%20two%20consecutive%20national%20elections%20with%20a%20huge%20majority%20-%20a%20grand%20achievement%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20for%20the%20RSS'%20ideology%2C%20once%20perceived%20as%20untouchable.%20Modi%20has%20undoubtedly%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20history%2C%20but%20he%20faced%20problems%20in%20some%20BJP-ruled%20states.%20Satraps%20like%20Vasundhara%2C%20Shivraj%2C%20Yediyurappa%2C%20and%20Raman%20Singh%20were%20once%20contemporaries%20of%20Modi%2C%20when%20he%20was%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Modi%20could%20not%20run%20these%20states%20the%20way%20he%20wanted.%20It's%20true%20that%20these%20leaders%20have%20never%20openly%20defied%20Modi%2C%20yet%20it%20was%20not%20smooth%20sailing.%20Modi%20did%20face%20subtle%20resistance%2C%20especially%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Rajasthan.%20As%20a%20leader%2C%20he%20believes%20in%20one-way%20traffic%3B%20there%20is%20no%20room%20for%20disagreement.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20said%20that%20the%20surprise%20choices%20in%20three%20states%20is%20an%20exercise%20to%20take%20total%20control%20of%20BJP-ruled%20states.%20It%20is%20fascinating%20how%20the%20stalwarts%20of%20the%20Atal-Advani%20era%20are%20walking%20into%20the%20sunset%2C%20soon%20to%20be%20part%20of%20nostalgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20every%20leader%20has%20a%20right%20to%20choose%20their%20team%20to%20implement%20their%20vision.%20It%20is%20for%20history%20to%20judge%20the%20merits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20characteristics%20of%20the%20Modi%20era%20is%20that%20journalists%20have%20restricted%20access%20to%20information.%20No%20wonder%20that%20theories%20get%20wings%20and%20speculation%20flies.%20That%20these%20are%20bold%20moves%20is%20irrefutable.%20Is%20it%20a%20masterstroke%3F%20The%20jury%20is%20out%2C%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702533720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Frj41o8tg_bhajan-lal-vishnu-deo-mohan-yadav-split-650_650x400_12_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F4-theories-to-explain-bjps-state-shockers-take-your-pick-4671270%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20theories%20are%20in%20circulation%20in%20journalistic%20circles%20and%20also%20in%20the%20power%20corridors%20on%20why%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20oblige%20its%20big%20leaders%20while%20choosing%20chief%20ministers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F4-theories-to-explain-bjps-state-shockers-take-your-pick-4671270%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F4-theories-to-explain-bjps-state-shockers-take-your-pick-4671270%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F4-theories-to-explain-bjps-state-shockers-take-your-pick-4671270%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Gaza%20war%3A%20What%20is%20the%20price%20of%20peace%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702533690000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA8CE%2Fproduction%2F_132041234_gettyimages-1801103706.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67701700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BBC's%20Jeremy%20Bowen%20asks%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20activists%20about%20their%20hopes%20for%20resolving%20the%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67701700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67701700.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67701700.am