22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MPhil%20Degree%2C%20No%20Job%3A%20Parliament%20Protester's%20Mother%20On%20Why%20She%20Was%20Upset%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20four%20protesters%20arrested%20for%20the%20parliament%20security%20breach%20was%20despondent%20as%20she%20was%20unemployed%2C%20her%20family%20said.%20Shocking%20scenes%20were%20witnessed%20during%20Zero%20Hour%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday%20when%20two%20men%2C%20Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20D%20Manoranjan%2C%20jumped%20out%20of%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20and%20into%20the%20chamber.%20One%20of%20them%20opened%20a%20yellow%20smoke%20canister%20and%20jumped%20from%20desk%20to%20desk%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20reach%20the%20Speaker's%20Chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20protesters%2C%20Neelam%20Azad%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%2C%20were%20caught%20releasing%20colour%20smoke%20from%20an%20aerosol%20canister%20on%20a%20road%20outside%20the%20Parliament.%20Neelam's%20family%20said%20that%20she%20had%20completed%20the%20research%20programme%20M.Phil%20and%20had%20also%20cleared%20central%20examinations%20mandatory%20to%20get%20a%20teaching%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20highly%20qualified%2C%20but%20wasn't%20getting%20a%20job.%20She%20was%20so%20stressed%20because%20of%20this%20that%20she%20often%20used%20to%20say%20that%20I%20should%20just%20die%20as%20despite%20studying%20so%20much%2C%20I%20am%20unable%20to%20earn%20two%20meals%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20mother%20Saraswati%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam's%20brother%2C%20Ramniwas%2C%20told%20reporters%20he%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20incident%20from%20one%20of%20their%20relatives%2C%20who%20dialled%20him%20to%20see%20the%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20studies%20in%20Hisar%20and%20is%20not%20linked%20with%20any%20political%20party.%20We%20don't%20know%20why%20she%20did%20that.%20We%20will%20know%20only%20after%20meeting%20her.%20We%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20incident%20from%20one%20of%20our%20brothers%2C%20who%20called%20us.%20She%20came%20home%20only%20two%20days%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramniwas%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Neelam%20had%20moved%20to%20Haryana's%20Jind%20to%20prepare%20for%20competitive%20exams%20as%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20get%20a%20job%20in%20Hisar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20had%20completed%20her%20BA%2C%20MA%2C%20M.%20Phil%20and%20had%20cleared%20NET%2C%20but%20was%20still%20unemployed.%20She%20moved%20to%20Jind%20six%20months%20ago%20and%20was%20preparing%20for%20the%20Secondary%20Teachers%20Eligibility%20Test%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamniwas%20said%20that%20she%20has%20often%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20at%20protests.%20She%20also%20took%20part%20in%20the%20year-long%20farmers%20protest%20near%20Delhi%20demanding%20the%20repeal%20of%20three%20farm%20bills.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoranjan's%20father%2C%20Devaraje%20Gowda%2C%20said%20if%20his%20son%20has%20done%20anything%20wrong%2C%20he%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bhanged%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20parliament%20is%20ours...%20Many%20people%20have%20built%20that%20temple%2C%20from%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20to%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru...%20It%20is%20not%20acceptable%20for%20someone%20to%20behave%20like%20this%20with%20the%20temple%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20my%20son%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gowda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lucknow%20resident%2C%20Sagar%20Sharma%2C%20has%20four%20members%20in%20his%20family%2C%20including%20him.%20He%20rides%20an%20e-rickshaw%20for%20a%20living.%20His%20family%20said%20he%20told%20them%20that%20he%20would%20be%20going%20to%20Delhi%20for%20two%20days%20to%20join%20a%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702530540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fgtnabtrk_neelam-lok-sabha-protester_625x300_14_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-security-breach-neelam-canister-woman-she