-king-shashi-tharoors-shoutout-to-mp-who-caught-lok-sabha-intruder-4670930%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20has%20praised%20his%20party%20colleague%20Gurjeet%20Singh%20Aujla%2C%20for%20restraining%20one%20of%20the%20two%20intruders%20who%20jumped%20from%20the%20Parliament%20visitor's%20gallery%20and%20set%20off%20smoke%20bombs%20inside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsingh-is-king-shashi-tharoors-shoutout-to-mp-who-caught-lok-sabha-intruder-4670930%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsingh-is-king-shashi-tharoors-shoutout-to-mp-who-caught-lok-sabha-intruder-4670930%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsingh-is-king-shashi-tharoors-shoutout-to-mp-who-caught-lok-sabha-intruder-4670930%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20'Bhagat%20Singh%20Fan%20Club'%2C%2018%20Months%20Of%20Planning%20Behind%20Parliament%20Breach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20stunning%20breach%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20a%20result%20of%20at%20least%2018%20months%20of%20meticulous%20planning%20and%20several%20meetings%20among%20the%20accused%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20hailed%20from%20different%20states%20but%20had%20one%20common%20link%20-%20a%20social%20media%20page%20called%20the%20'Bhagat%20Singh%20Fan%20Club'%2C%20police%20officials%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20scenes%2C%20which%20unfolded%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Parliament%20attack%20in%202001%2C%20saw%20Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D%20jumping%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20into%20the%20chamber%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20Zero%20Hour%2C%20around%201%20pm.%20Both%20deployed%20canisters%20containing%20yellow%20smoke%20and%20Sharma%20jumped%20over%20desks%20towards%20the%20Speaker's%20Chair%20before%20he%20was%20overpowered%20by%20MPs%20and%20beaten%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20Parliament%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20Neelam%20Azad%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%20used%20canisters%20with%20yellow%20and%20red%20smoke%20and%20shouted%20slogans%20against%20%26quot%3Bdictatorship%26quot%3B.%20While%20Sharma%20is%20a%20Lucknow%20resident%2C%20Manoranjan%20is%20from%20Mysore%2C%20Neelam%20is%20from%20Jind%20in%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Shinde%20is%20from%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20two%20accused%20are%20Lalit%20Jha%2C%20who%20allegedly%20shot%20videos%20of%20Neelam%20and%20Shinde%20using%20the%20canisters%20outside%20Parliament%20and%20then%20fled%20with%20their%20cellphones%2C%20and%20Vicky%20Sharma%2C%20in%20whose%20house%20the%20other%20accused%20stayed%20before%20the%20attack.%20Lalit%20Jha%20is%20from%20Bihar%20while%20Vicky%20Sharma%20is%20from%20Gurgaon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeetings%2C%20Recce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20investigation%20so%20far%2C%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20accused%20took%20place%20in%20Mysuru%20around%2018%20months%20ago.%20It%20was%20at%20this%20meeting%20that%20they%20talked%20about%20various%20ways%20of%20highlighting%20issues%20which%20they%20believed%20Parliament%20should%20discuss%2C%20including%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%20and%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20meeting%20was%20held%20nine%20months%20ago%2C%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20and%20that%20was%20when%20a%20detailed%20plan%20began%20to%20take%20shape%2C%20police%20officials%20said.%20This%20meeting%20took%20place%20near%20Chandigarh%20airport%2C%20during%20the%20protest%20by%20farmers%20to%20demand%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20the%20minimum%20support%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20four%20months%20after%20this%2C%20in%20July%2C%20Sharma%20went%20to%20New%20Delhi%20from%20Lucknow%20to%20conduct%20a%20reconnaissance%20of%20the%20Parliament%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20before%20the%20first%20session%20was%20held%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%20in%20September%2C%20and%20Sharma%20could%20not%20get%20access.%20Officials%20said%20he%20carried%20out%20a%20recce%20of%20the%20building%20from%20outside%2C%20took%20note%20of%20all%20the%20security%20arrangements%20and%20reported%20back%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGathering%2C%20Canister%20Distribution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20decided%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Parliament%20attack%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20breach%2C%20Sharma%2C%20Manoranjan%2C%20Neelam%20and%20Shinde%20reached%20Delhi%20on%20Sunday%2C%20December%2010%2C%20and%20headed%20to%20Vicky%20Sharma's%20house%20in%20Gurgaon%2C%20where%20they%20stayed%20until%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20official%20said%20that%2C%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20breach%2C%20the%20accused%20gathered%20at%20India%20Gate%20and%20this%20was%20where%20Shinde%20distributed%20the%20canisters%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20accused.%20He%20had%20procured%20the%20canisters%20from%20his%20hometown%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20carried%20them%20with%20him%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20plan%20involved%20all%20six%20going%20inside%20the%20Parliament%2C%20but%20they%20had%20managed%20to%20get%20passes%20only%20for%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArrests%2C%20Security%20Concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation%2C%20and%20several%20MPs%20have%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20intruders%20managing%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20breach%20on%20a%20day%20when%20security%20inside%20the%20Parliament%20was%20already%20tight%2C%20given%20that%20it%20was%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20attack.%20Security%20agencies%20would%20have%20also%20been%20alert%20since%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20had%20threatened%20to%20attack%20the%20Parliament%20'on%20or%20before%20December%2013'.%20No%20link%20has%2C%20however%2C%20been%20established%20between%20Pannun's%20threat%20and%20the%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20entered%20the%20Parliament%20complex%20around%20noon%20and%20jumped%20into%20the%20chamber%20around%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20officials%20said.%20They%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20along%20with%20Neelam%20and%20Shinde%2C%20and%20Vicky%20Sharma%20and%20his%20wife%20have%20been%20detained.%20Lalit%20Jha%20ran%20away%20with%20the%20cellphones%20of%20everyone%20involved%20in%20the%20breach%20after%20shooting%20some%20videos%20of%20Neelam%20and%20Shinde%20deploying%20the%20canisters%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20on%20to%20trace%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20people%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20the%20stringent%20anti-terror%20law%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20as%20well%20as%20sections%20related%20to%20criminal%20conspiracy%20and%20promoting%20enmity%2C%20among%20others%2C%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20They%20are%20all%20being%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702528140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F9fckduto_parliament-smoke-attack-_625x300_13_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-breach-parliament-security-breach-a-bhagat-singh-fan-club-18-months-of-planning-behind-parliament-breach-4670793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stunning%20breach%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20a%20result%20of%20at%20least%2018%20months%20of%20meticulous%20planning%20and%20several%20meetings%20among%20the%20accused%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20had%20one%20common%20link%20-%20a%20social%20media%20page%20called%20the%20'Bhagat%20Singh%20Fan%20Club'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-breach-parliament-secur