s%E2%80%99s%20T.N.%20Prathapan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESecurity%20breach!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FParliament%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYZhPg1Kv97%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYZhPg1Kv97%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Satish%20Acharya%20(%40satishacharya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsatishacharya%2Fstatus%2F1735118745427943435%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20has%2C%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20written%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20new%20protocols%20and%20an%20overall%20review%20of%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20be%20undertaken%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20a%20report%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaker%20Om%20Birla%20had%20called%20a%20meeting%20after%20the%20breach%2C%20in%20which%20House%20leaders%20had%20suggested%20that%20full-body%20scanners%2C%20glass%20walls%20in%20front%20of%20visitors%E2%80%99%20galleries%20and%20security%20guards%20be%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20preliminary%20inquiry%20has%20it%20that%20the%20post%20of%20the%20joint%20secretary%20of%20security%20has%20been%20vacant%20for%20over%20a%20month%2C%20after%20IPS%20officer%20Raghubir%20Lal%20was%20transferred%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%2C%20quoting%20unnamed%20sources%2C%20that%20the%20preliminary%20inquiry%20has%20also%20unveiled%20%E2%80%9Ca%20number%20of%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20including%20a%20grouse%20levelled%20by%20the%20parliament%20security%20staff%20that%20the%20number%20of%20visitor%20gallery%20passes%20issued%20on%20MPs%E2%80%99%20recommendation%20has%20increased%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFour%20held%20under%20UAPA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20out%20of%20the%20six%20people%20who%20were%20behind%20the%20parliament%20breach%20have%20been%20held%20and%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20sections%2016%20and%2018%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fparliament-security-breach-arrested-uapa-9067561%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20have%20also%20been%20charged%20under%20sections%20153%20(want%20only%20giving%20provocation%20with%20an%20intent%20to%20cause%20riot)%2C%20120-B%20(criminal%20conspiracy)%2C%20452%20(trespass)%2C%20186%20(obstructing%20public%20servant%20in%20discharge%20of%20public%20functions)%2C%20353%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20deter%20public%20servants%20from%20discharge%20of%20his%20duty)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20said%20that%20Sagar%20Sharma%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Manoranjan%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20Amol%20Shinde%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20Neelam%20Azad%20and%20Vishal%20Sharma%20from%20Haryana%2C%20were%20upset%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20jobs%20and%20the%20rise%20in%20prices.%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20none%20were%20affiliated%20to%20any%20political%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20five%20were%20between%2023%20and%2042%20years%20old.%20One%20of%20them%20had%20been%20part%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20and%20the%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20agitation.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Neelam%2C%20had%20three%20degrees%20and%20had%20cleared%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702528136000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14095043%2FGBN2cf7b