e%2C%20where%20perfectly%20manicured%20lawns%20competed%20with%20the%20sheen%20of%20tightly%20stretched%20silk%20sheets%20across%20the%20immense%20four-poster%20bed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20353px)%2085vw%2C%20353px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13164529%2Fthe-viceroys-artist_FC-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13164529%2Fthe-viceroys-artist_FC-1.jpg%20772w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13164529%2Fthe-viceroys-artist_FC-1-193x300.jpg%20193w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13164529%2Fthe-viceroys-artist_FC-1-659x1024.jpg%20659w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689058%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22549%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnindyo%20Roy%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Viceroy%E2%80%99s%20Artist%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EHachette%20India%20(December%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMal%20de%20barquement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20the%20phrase%20Lord%20Northbrook%2C%20his%20host%2C%20had%20used%20to%20explain%20why%20%E2%80%93%20even%20after%20four%20weeks%20%E2%80%93%20Lear%20still%20felt%20that%20he%20had%20not%20left%20the%20boat.%20Surprisingly%2C%20however%2C%20that%20feeling%20dissipated%20almost%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20horse%20cart%20departed%20from%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edak%20bungalow%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20foothills%20of%20Pankhabari%20and%20made%20its%20way%20up%20a%20steep%2C%20curving%20road%2C%20depositing%20him%2C%20his%20eleven%20items%20of%20luggage%20and%20manservant%20eight%20hours%20later%20outside%20a%20dimly%20lit%20cottage%20in%20Kurseong.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20stiffness%20around%20his%20ankles%20and%20thighs%20reminds%20him%20of%20the%20seemingly%20unending%20ride%20up%20the%20hills%20the%20day%20before.%20Trundling%20all%20day%20long%20through%20narrow%2C%20winding%20roads%20lined%20with%20pine%20and%20bamboo%2C%20the%20pony%20cart%20had%20left%20him%20under%20the%20crumbling%20porch%20of%20a%20thatched%20stone%20house.%20This%20was%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edak%20bungalow%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20Kurseong%E2%80%99s%20Weathercock%20Point.%20After%20clambering%20up%20the%20steps%20in%20the%20dark%20to%20the%20front%20gallery%2C%20he%20was%20cheered%20by%20the%20sight%20of%20two%20oil%20lamps%20sitting%20on%20top%20of%20a%20broken%20mantelpiece.%20The%20air%20was%20icy%20cold.%20The%20spluttering%20fire%20in%20the%20fireplace%2C%20visible%20at%20the%20far%20end%20of%20the%20room%2C%20presented%20a%20scene%20that%20he%20had%20only%20encountered%20in%20books%20read%20long%2C%20long%20ago.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Castle%20of%20Otranto%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20yes%2C%20that%20was%20it.%20The%20shadows%20swaying%20almost%20imperceptibly%20behind%20the%20heavy%20curtains%C2%A0%20that%20reeked%20of%20damp%20and%20decay%20were%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20pages%20of%20a%20gothic%20masterpiece.%20The%20perfect%20abode%20of%20unquiet%20spirits%2C%20geckos%20and%20bats%2C%20not%20to%20speak%20of%20strange%20housekeepers%20with%20wizened%2C%20pale%C2%A0%20faces%20and%20dressed%20in%20dark%2C%20flowing%20gowns.%20As%20he%20passed%20through%20the%20narrow%20corridor%20beyond%20the%20gallery%20door%2C%20he%20noticed%20the%20passing%20draught%20lifting%20the%20covers%20on%20the%20mantelpiece.%20The%20doors%20trembled%20intermittently.%20Giorgi%2C%20his%20manservant%2C%20went%20about%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebusiness%20unperturbed%2C%20lifting%20the%20bags%20and%20carrying%20them%20to%20the%20room%20before%20vanishing%20into%20the%20darkness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20lying%20still%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20Lear%20strains%20his%20eyes%20at%20the%20small%20window%20to%20catch%20any%20sign%20of%20light%2C%20but%20the%20darkness%20outside%20hangs%20like%20an%20impenetrable%20black%20curtain.%20No%20one%20had%20warned%20him%20that%20his%20destination%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edak%20bungalow%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20which%20he%20had%20travelled%20thousands%20of%20miles%2C%20all%20the%20way%20from%20the%20port%20of%20Genoa%20through%20the%20heart%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20would%20be%20a%20forbidding%20three%20room%20thatched%20cottage%20with%20plaster%20crumbling%20from%20large%20portions%20of%20the%20lime-washed%20walls.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20shred%20of%20viceregality%20visible%20anywhere!%20The%20three-day%20journey%20from%20Calcutta%20to%20Kurseong%20reminded%20him%20of%20the%20time%20when%20his%20little%20fingers%20felt%20a%20loosely%20coiled%20and%20knotted%20skein%20that%20he%20had%20once%20found%20in%20an%20old%20attic%20chest.%20The%20exhaustion%20of%20being%20on%20slow%20Indian%20trains%2C%20clanking%20along%2C%20and%20on%20even%20slower%20pony%20carts%20could%20only%20be%20matched%20by%20the%20many%20sensations%20that%20surged%20through%20his%20heavy%20eyes%20and%20ears.%20The%20unexpected%20transitions%20from%20suffocating%20heat%20to%20numbing%20cold%3B%20the%20gaggle%20of%20early-morning%20workers%20on%20the%20streets%20outside%20train%20stations%20girding%20themselves%20for%20work%3B%20the%20long-drawn%20half%20understood%20conversations%20with%20colonial%20officials%20and%20interminable%20verbal%20exchanges%20with%20native%20Indians%20about%20directions%20or%20monetary%20payments%3B%20the%20pungent%20odours%20rising%20from%20broths%20served%20on%20frail%20pale%20blue%20china.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWere%20his%20travels%20worth%20the%20pain%20and%20tedium%20that%20he%20now%20feels%20throbbing%20in%20his%20bones%3F%20Would%20Kurseong%20offer%20a%20view%20of%20the%20mighty%20Kanchenjunga%20that%20he%20can%20capture%20on%20just%20an%20ordinary%20sheet%20of%20paper%20by%20merely%20using%20a%20graphite%20pencil%20bought%20from%20an%20old%20shop%20in%20Genoa%3F%20Had%20he%20perhaps%20been%20too%20ambitious%20in%20hoping%20to%20turn%20a%20simple%20pencil%20sketch%20into%20an%20oil%20painting%20that%20was%20worthy%20of%20being%20hung%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20viceregal%20rooms%3F%20Would%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epainting%20ever%20be%20able%20to%20match%20the%20splendour%20of%20floors%20covered%20with%20the%20most%20expensive%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esumac%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Erugs.%20Had%20the%20handsome%20commission%20promised%20by%20the%20Viceroy%20of%20India%20been%20the%20lure%20that%20had%20brought%20him%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20winter%2C%20to%20these%20remote%20mountains%3F%20He%20knew%20that%20the%20offer%20had%20come%20after%20years%20of%20quiet%20anticipation%20as%20he%20saw%20the%20years%20slipping%20by%20and%20arthritis%20beginning%20to%20trouble%20his%20knees.%20All%20along%2C%20he%20had%20known%20that%20his%20decision%20had%20been%20driven%20by%20an%20unnameable%20need%20to%20escape.%20But%20escape%20from%20what%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20excerpt%20from%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Viceroy%E2%80%99s%20Artist%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eby%20Anindyo%20Roy%20is%20republished%20with%20permission%20from%20Hachette%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnindyo%20Roy%20is%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20at%20Colby%20College.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702524630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13165147%2Fkangchenjunga-nroerich-cdb52c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fexcerpt-anindyo-roy-the-viceroys-artist%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Were%20his%20travels%20worth%20the%20pain%