0in%20America%20don't%20lead%20with%20these%20types%20of%20personal%20or%20political%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20unfamiliar%20with%20certain%20customs%2C%20such%20as%20handing%20out%20business%20cards%20with%20both%20hands%2C%20often%20with%20a%20slight%20head%20nod.%20This%20practice%20was%20part%20of%20nearly%20every%20business-related%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20giving%20birth%20and%20landing%20a%20full-time%20job%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20time%20there%2C%20I%20had%20so%20many%20business%20cards%20from%20such%20exchanges%20that%20I%20could%20have%20tossed%20them%20in%20the%20air%20like%20confetti%20during%20the%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20ball%20drop%20at%20Times%20Square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20despite%20these%20types%20of%20cultural%20adjustments%2C%20Singapore%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20lovely%20place%20I%20imagined%20it%20would%20be%2C%20in%20large%20part%20because%20of%20the%20warm%20people%20%E2%80%94%20both%20citizens%20and%20non%20%E2%80%94%20who%20welcomed%20my%20son%20and%20me%20with%20open%20arms.%20When%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20my%20Florida%20hometown%20seven%20years%20later%2C%20Singapore%20felt%20as%20much%20like%20%26quot%3Bhome%26quot%3B%20as%20New%20York%20had%20before%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20wasn't%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexpecting%3F%20Feeling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-reverse-culture-shock-is-and-how-to-deal-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereverse%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20shock%20so%20acutely.%20Sure%2C%20I%20had%20lived%20in%20the%20US%20most%20of%20my%20life%20and%20spoke%20the%20language%2C%20but%20everything%20from%20transportation%20to%20tipping%20and%20wellness%20treatments%20felt%20foreign.%20Here's%20what%20it's%20been%20like%20being%20back%2C%20first%20in%20Florida%20and%20now%20in%20Colorado%2C%20for%20the%20last%20year%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20around%20took%20some%20getting%20used%20to%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfi