t%20the%20man%20and%20a%20separate%20woman%20tried%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20evidence%20after%20the%20boy's%20death.%20The%20car%20was%20found%20%26quot%3Bburned-out%20and%20abandoned%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20field%20in%20Lansing%2C%20Michigan%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20in%20their%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20barrel%20of%20the%20gun%20used%20in%20the%20shooting%20was%20later%20found%20disassembled%20in%20the%20walls%20of%20a%20house%20in%20the%20town%2C%20per%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20online%20court%20records%2C%20the%20man's%20attorney%20stopped%20working%20for%20him%20on%20Tuesday.%20No%20new%20attorney%20information%20has%20been%20posted%20in%20the%20court%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFirearms%20are%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20children%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20noted%20that%20Americans%2C%20especially%20children%2C%20are%20facing%20an%20epidemic%20of%20gun%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20far%20too%20many%20senseless%2C%20preventable%20deaths%20because%20of%20children%20having%20access%20to%20firearms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ingham%20County%20prosecuting%20attorney%20John%20J.%20Dewane.%20%26quot%3BNo%20child%20should%20ever%20have%20access%20to%20a%20loaded%20firearm.%20No%20child%20should%20ever%20be%20in%20danger%20of%20being%20shot%20under%20any%20circumstances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2Fnejmc2201761%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20New%20England%20Journal%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202021%20was%20the%20first%20year%20in%20which%20firearms%20were%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20children%20and%20young%20adults%20ages%201%20to%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20mass%20shootings%20make%20headlines%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20gun%20deaths%20in%202022%20were%20the%20result%20of%20suicide%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fviolenceprevention%2Ffirearms%2Ffastfact.html%5C%22%20targ