%20this%20example%20it%20started%20at%20%241%2C600%20a%20drop.%20At%2012%20drops%20that%20would%20be%20%2419%2C200.%20To%20run%20them%20would%20take%20two%20people%20maybe%208%20hours%20or%20so.%20I%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20spend%20a%20Saturday%20doing%20this%20with%20you%20and%20splitting%20%2419%2C200.%20Basically%20that%20price%20is%20highway%20robbery.%20Why%20did%20we%20get%20robbed%3F%20Because%20no%20one%20worried%20about%20the%20cost.%20That%20%241%2C600%20became%20%24800%20and%20then%20%24300%20as%20some%20questions%20were%20asked%20and%20negotiations%20ensued.%20We%20have%20this%20this%20type%20of%20problem%20in%20many%20places%20-%20we%20need%20to%20root%20them%20out.%20And%20we%20need%20everyone%20who%20is%20at%20Wayfair%20to%20care.%20If%20you%20see%20wasted%20spend%20that%20you%20do%20not%20know%20how%20to%20fix%20just%20let%20me%20know%20and%20I%20will%20help.%20This%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20strengthen%20the%20culture.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnd%20lastly%20I%20want%20to%20encourage%20us%20all%20to%20be%20smart.%20You%20will%20encounter%20some%20things%20that%20do%20not%20make%20sense.%20Question%20them.%20And%20then%20escalate%20it%20if%20you%20encounter%20bureaucracy%20and%20believe%20that%20you%20are%20right.%20We%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20policies%20or%20practices%20that%20need%20to%20refreshed%2C%20leaned%20out%2C%20or%20eliminated.%20Less%20is%20more%20-%20lets%20find%20policies%20and%20procedures%20that%20do%20not%20add%20value%20and%20eliminate%20them.%20Lets%20find%20policies%20that%20do%20not%20make%20sense%20and%20adjust%20them.%20And%20just%20approach%20everything%20with%20first%20principles.%20You%20are%20smart%20-%20bet%20on%20that%20and%20use%20your%20judgment.%20And%20feel%20free%20to%20ask%20me%20or%20other%20leaders%20for%20advice%20when%20you%20have%20a%20question.%20This%20will%20help%20us%20all%20win.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETogether%20we%20can%20win%20much%20faster%20than%20we%20are%20winning%20now%20i