ots-review%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.everlane.com%252Fproducts%252Fwomens-rain-boot-stone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEverlane's%20%2485%20rain%20boot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%C2%A0comes%20in%20four%20neutral%20colors%20(surplus%2C%20black%2C%20toffee%2C%20and%20pink)%2C%20and%20whole%20sizes.%20Right%20now%2C%20it's%20only%20available%20on%20the%20women's%20portion%20of%20the%20site%2C%20but%20men%20could%20conceivably%20get%20their%20own%20pair%20with%20a%20little%20help%20from%20the%20company's%20live%20chat%20box%20for%20size%20conversion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20the%20Rain%20Boot%20is%20designed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223847%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20putting%20on%20the%20Everlane%20black%20rubber%20rain%20boots.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c57664185aef53d0d5c3464%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222885%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEverlane's%20Rain%20Boot%20has%20pull%20tabs%20that%20make%20them%20easier%20to%20slip%20on.%3Cp%3EEverlane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20team's%20goal%20was%20simple%3A%20make%20the%20most%20comfortable%20rain%20boot%20possible.%20The%20result%20is%20a%20%2475%20rain%20boot%20that%20has%20a%20versatile%20ankle%20height%2C%20grippy%20tread%2C%20and%20a%20custom-designed%20cushioned%20insole%20for%20bouncy%20comfort.%20The%20stretch%20panels%20and%20pull%20tabs%20make%20them%20easier%20to%20throw%20on%20and%20off%2C%20and%20the%20rubber%20is%20flexible%20and%20easy%20to%20clean.%20They've%20got%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20thick%2C%20wintry%20socks%2C%20and%20black%20rubber%20reinforcements%20at%20the%20front%20for%20extra%20coverage%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20style%20points.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20their%20official%20launch%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20tested%20Everlane's%20new%20%2485%20rain%20boots%20in%20the%20grimy%20slush%20and%20rain%20of%20New%20York%20City.%20We%20stomped%20through%20puddles%2C%20ran%20to%20catch%20trains%2C%20and%20rushed%20through%20hectic%20weekdays%20at%20the%20office.%20Before%20you%20buy%20a%20pair%2C%20we've%20compiled%20our%20thoughts%20on%20them%20below%2C%20including%20an%20update%20to%20how%20they're%20holding%20up%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWe%20tried%20Everlane's%20%2485%20rain%20boots.%20Read%20our%20first%20impressions%20and%20two-year%20updates%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESurplus%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Everlane%20Rain%20Boots%20in%20the%20Surplus%20color.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c5766e4b357333809026664%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEverlane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20impression%20(February%202019)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rain%20boots%20are%20typically%20so%20big%2C%20clunky%2C%20stiff%2C%20and%20ugly%20that%20I%20don't%20wear%20them.%20I%20usually%20just%20pull%20on%20some%20Doc%20Martens%20and%20try%20to%20avoid%20deep%20puddles.%20Everlane's%20rain%20boots%20are%20made%20of%20such%20soft%2C%20flexible%20real%20rubber%20that%20they%20bend%20with%20you%20and%20feel%20like%20super%20comfortable%20shoes.%20The%20traction%20on%20the%20bottom%20sole%20is%20fantastic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20key%20for%20slippery%20wet%20surfaces%20that%20can%20be%20treacherous%20like%20stairs%20and%20the%20subway%20platform.%20These%20boots%20actually%20look%20cool%2C%20too%2C%20which%20isn't%20something%20I%20thought%20I'd%20say%20about%20a%20rain%20boot.%20I%20ordered%20my%20normal%20boot%20size%20%E2%80%94%208%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20were%20slightly%20big%2C%20which%20I%20liked%20because%20I%20can%20wear%20thick%20socks%20with%20them.%20The%20rise%20of%20the%20boot%20is%20fairly%20short%2C%20though%2C%20so%20you%20need%20to%20judge%20puddle%20depth%20carefully%20or%20risk%20wet%20feet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo-year%20update%20(March%202021)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEverlane's%20Rain%20Boot%20is%20just%20about%20the%20perfect%20rain%20boot%2C%20so%20I've%20worn%20it%20just%20about%20whenever%20rain%20is%20in%20the%20forecast.%20They%20remain%20comfortable%20and%20impervious%20to%20water.%20I%20love%20the%20thick%20soles%20and%20their%20grippy%20texture.%20I%20have%20to%20wear%20thick%20socks%20with%20mine%2C%20though%2C%20so%20they%20are%20not%20ideal%20for%20the%20summer%20months.%20I%20don't%20wear%20them%20during%20summer%20rainstorms%20because%20they%20really%20trap%20heat%20and%20make%20my%20feet%20hot.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Malarie%20Gokey%2C%20deputy%20editor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EToffee%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Everlane%20rain%20boot%20in%20the%20Toffee%20color.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c57671d85aef53d0d5c3466%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEverlane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20impression%20(February%202019)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble%20with%20rain%20boots.%20I'm%20just%20over%205-foot-1%2C%20so%20shorter%20boots%20tend%20to%20make%20my%20legs%20look%20stubby%2C%20and%20taller%20boots%20tend%20to%20be%20totally%20overwhelming%20on%20my%20frame.%20Everlane%20has%20somehow%20perfectly%20mastered%20the%20height%20of%20their%20boots%2C%20and%20they%20cut%20off%20in%20just%20the%20right%20spot%20to%20not%20make%20my%20legs%20look%20like%20short%20little%20sausages.%20Thanks%20to%20a%20slit%20in%20the%20rubber%20that's%20covered%20by%20elastic%20panels%20on%20the%20side%2C%20the%20boots%20have%20a%20flexible%20shaft%20that%20doesn't%20chafe%20your%20legs%20%E2%80%94%20an%20issue%20I've%20had%20with%20every%20past%20pair%20of%20rain%20boots%20I've%20tried.%20The%20cushioned%20insert%20is%20also%20extremely%20comfy%2C%20so%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20can%20actually%20wear%20these%20all%20day%20and%20not%20just%20change%20into%20backup%20shoes%20once%20I%20get%20to%20the%20office.%20Oh%2C%20and%20I%20recommend%20sizing%20up%20if%20you're%20a%20half%20size.%20More%20room%20for%20warm%20socks!%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Sally%20Kapan%2C%20deputy%20editor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo-year%20update%20(March%202021)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'm%20a%20huge%20proponent%20of%20rain%20boots%20as%20snow%20boots%20%E2%80%94%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fshearling-insoles-review%5C%22%3Eadd%20a%20shearling%20insole%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20they're%20suddenly%20warm%20enough%20for%2030-degree%20weather.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20I've%20done%20with%20my%20Everlane%20rain%20boots%2C%20which%20are%20a%20staple%20of%20my%20cold-weather%20wardrobe.%20They've%20held%20up%20incredibly%20well%20over%20time%20and%20they%20still%20look%20new%2C%20which%20is%20probably%20because%20they're%20easy%20to%20keep%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cushy%20sole%20is%20an%20outstanding%20feature%20of%20this%20style%20(something%20that's%20hard%20to%20come%20by%20with%20solid%20rubber%20boots)%20and%20I'm%20pleased%20to%20say%20that%20it's%20not%20lost%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20insoles.%20Plus%2C%20they're%20easy%20to%20wear%20with%20everything%20from%20jeans%20to%20flowy%20fall%20dresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPink%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Everlane%20rain%20boots%20in%20the%20pink%20color.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c576707a2651639122cab32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEverlane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20impression%20(February%202019)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20noticed%20about%20these%20boots%20is%20how%20roomy%20and%20comfortable%20they%20are.%20Everlane%20definitely%20understands%20that%20thicker%20socks%20are%20the%20norm%20in%20cold%2C%20rainy%20weather%2C%20so%20rest%20assured%20your%20regular%20shoe%20size%20(or%20a%20half%20size%20up)%20will%20work%20fine.%20Light-colored%20rain%20boots%20can%20seem%20like%20a%20bad%20decision%20as%20you%20walk%20through%20dirty%20conditions%2C%20but%20Everlane's%20were%20easy%20to%20wipe%20down%2C%20plus%20the%20toe%20%E2%80%94%20which%20often%20endures%20the%20bulk%20of%20encounters%20with%20puddles%20and%20other%20grimy%20obstacles%20%E2%80%94%20has%20a%20black%20rubber%20reinforcement.%20The%20thick%2C%20sturdy%20exterior%20and%20soles%20made%20me%20confident%20to%20wear%20them%20in%20a%20rainstorm%2C%20but%20the%20comfort%20factor%20and%20cute%20color%20convinced%20me%20to%20keep%20them%20on%20throughout%20the%20day.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Connie%20Chen%2C%20senior%20reporter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo-year%20update%20(March%202021)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThough%20they're%20a%20tad%20heavy%20for%20my%20taste%2C%20these%20boots%20really%20are%20my%20most%20practical.%20As%20I've%20worn%20them%20more%2C%20the%20features%20I've%20come%20to%20appreciate%20the%20most%20are%20the%20black%20rubber%20reinforcements%20at%20the%20toe%20and%20the%20pull%20tabs%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20shoe.%20The%20black%20rubber%20protects%20the%20pretty%20blush%20color%2C%20while%20the%20tabs%20make%20the%20boots%20easy%20to%20slip%20on%20whenever%20I%20need%20to%20rush%20out%20the%20door%20(which%20feels%20like%20most%20days).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBlack%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Everlane%20rain%20boots%20in%20the%20black%20color.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c57679ee43f40396b069f46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEverlane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20impression%20(February%202019)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20hate%20ruining%20my%20favorite%20shoes%20in%20the%20rain%2C%20but%20I've%20yet%20to%20find%20a%20pair%20of%20rain%20boots%20I%20actually%20like%20to%20wear.%20At%20least%20that%20was%20the%20case%20before%20I%20tried%20these%20boots.%20In%20black%2C%20they%20look%20like%20a%20regular%20pair%20of%20casual%2C%20Chelsea%20boots.%20They're%20roomy%20enough%20to%20wear%20with%20thick%20socks%2C%20which%20is%20nice%20for%20cold%20days%2C%20but%20even%20with%20thin%20Peds%2C%20these%20fit%20just%20right.%20There's%20a%20soft%2C%20cushioned%20insert%20inside%20the%20shoe%20which%20is%20so%20comfortable%20%E2%80%94%20more%20so%20than%20most%20of%20my%20actual%20winter%20boots.%20They're%20also%20super%20easy%20to%20slip%20on%20and%20off%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20struggle%20with%20other%20rubber%20rain%20boots%20since%20they%20tend%20to%20get%20hot%20and%20sticky.%20These%20do%20their%20job%20of%20being%20great%20rain%20boots%2C%20but%20what%20I%20love%20most%20about%20them%20is%20that%20they%20actually%20look%20cool%2C%20too.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20feel%20embarrassed%20showing%20up%20to%20work%20in%20knee-high%2C%20ill-fitting%20polka%20dot%20rubber%20boots%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20actually%20wear%20these%20on%20a%20rainy%20day%2C%20indoor%20and%20out%2C%20and%20feel%20good%20about%20it.%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Remi%20Rosmarin%2C%20former%20reporter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne-year%20update%20(January%202020)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI've%20recommended%20this%20rain%20boot%20to%20so%20many%20people%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20I%20love%20the%20chunky%2C%20Chelsea%20boot%20look%20%E2%80%94%20it%20makes%20them%20feel%20appropriate%20for%20all%20sorts%20of%20occasions.%20The%20interior%20is%20soft%20and%20cushy%2C%20the%20thick%20soles%20are%20puddle-friendly%2C%20and%20the%20calf%20is%20pretty%20wide%2C%20which%20all%20work%20together%20to%20make%20these%20really%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20one%20to%20wear%20rain%20boots%20for%20anything%20other%20than%20outdoor%20activities%20that%20require%20them%2C%20but%2C%20these%20have%20changed%20me.%20I'll%20even%20wear%20these%20on%20days%20when%20the%20chance%20of%20rain%20is%20low%E2%80%94%20they're%20cute%20and%20comfortable%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20feel%20silly%20wearing%20them%20even%20if%20it%20doesn't%20rain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Feverlane-women-rain-boots-review%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702504366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F605b80d60d155e0019ef683f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Feverlane-women-rain-boots-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We've%20been%20wearing%20Everlane's%20%2485%20rain%20boots%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20Here's%20how%20they've%20held%20up%20over%20time%2C%20and%20what%20to%20know%20about%20the%20sizing%20and%20fit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mleighton%40insider.com%20(Mara%20Leighton)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Feverlane-women-rain-boots-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cocomelon%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20things%20on%20Netflix.%20Kids%20watched%20more%20than%20600%20million%20hours.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cocomelon%20character%20mascot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a0e217a3c8094d5dcad78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BJJ%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20baby%20who%20is%20the%20main%20character%20of%20Cocomelon.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Keeble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-reveals-viewership-da