asn't%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Artisan%20mixer%3B%20the%20large%20bowl%20felt%20open%20enough%20that%20I%20could%20scrape%20the%20sides%20without%20adjusting%20the%20head.%20The%20bowl%20also%20has%20a%20sturdy%20handle%20for%20easy%20lifting%2C%20and%20provided%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20pouring%20in%20ingredients%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20helpful%20when%20adding%20more%20than%20five%20cups%20of%20mix-ins%20for%20Compost%20Cookies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20shook%20a%20bit%20when%20I%20made%20bagel%20dough%2C%20it%20was%20never%20overly%20noisy%20and%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20had%20to%20babysit%20it%20for%20fear%20of%20it%20walking%20off%20the%20counter.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20would%20make%20multiple%20batches%20of%20bagels%20in%20a%20row%20to%20avoid%20overheating%20the%20mixer's%20lower-powered%20motor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20model%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fkitchenaid-stand-mixer-customization-tool%5C%22%3Eoffers%20customization%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20choose%20from%20almost%2050%20color%20options%2C%20engrave%20your%20stand%20mixer%2C%20or%20switch%20out%20the%20standard%20bowl%20for%20a%20patterned%20ceramic%20or%20glass%20mixing%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20initial%20testing%2C%20we've%20continued%20to%20use%20this%20model%20at%20least%20once%20a%20week.%20It's%20worked%20its%20way%20through%20pierogi%20dough%20and%20filling%2C%20multiple%20babkas%2C%20and%20many%20batches%20of%20holiday%20cookies%2C%20and%20still%20functions%20as%20well%20(and%20looks%20as%20good)%20as%20it%20did%20when%20I%20first%20received%20it.%20We'll%20continue%20to%20use%20this%20model%20regularly%20and%20report%20on%20its%20long-term%20durability.%20Overall%2C%20this%20is%20a%20great%20option%20for%20beginner%20bakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fkitchenaid-artisan-stand-mixer-review%5C%22%3EKitchenAid%20Artisan%20Stand%20Mixer%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20KitchenAid%20Classic%20Plus%204.5%20Quart%20Tilt-Head%20Stand%20Mixer%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f99d75969331a0011bc5e56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20an%20occasional%20or%20beginner%20baker%2C%20the%20KitchenAid%20Classic%20Plus%204.5%20Quart%20Tilt-Head%20Stand%20Mixer%20is%20a%20great%20model%20to%20begin%20with.%20It's%20made%20with%20the%20same%20metal%20parts%20as%20more%20expensive%20KitchenAid%20stand%20mixers%2C%20has%20a%20strong%20motor%2C%20and%20a%20relatively%20roomy%20work%20bowl.%20While%20on%20the%20smaller%20side%2C%20it%20still%20easily%20accommodates%20single%20batches%20of%20common%20recipes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20KitchenAid%20Classic%20Plus%C2%A0was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20my%20first%20mixer.%20I%20used%20it%20heavily%20for%20about%20five%20years%20until%20it%20gave%20out%20on%20me%20while%20kneading%20dough%20for%20hand-pulled%20noodles%20(a%20notoriously%20tricky%20dough%2C%20and%20one%20known%20to%20tax%20stand%20mixers).%20This%20issue%20first%20highlighted%20to%20me%20how%20most%20stand%20mixers%20break%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20choosing%20a%20model%20built%20for%20your%20typical%20usage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20a%20new%20version%20of%20this%20mixer%20for%20this%20guide%2C%20and%20while%20it%20happily%20worked%20through%20cookies%2C%20egg%20whites%2C%20and%20even%20hefty%20bagel%20dough%20without%20issue%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20with%20too%20much%20heavy%20use%2C%20like%20making%20many%20batches%20of%20bagel%20or%20pizza%20dough%20back-to-back%2C%20the%20mixer%20can%20overheat%20or%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20case%20of%20my%20old%20mixer%20%E2%80%94%20wear%20down%20its%20gears.%20While%20the%20issue%20is%20repairable%2C%20it%20requires%20seeing%20a%20KitchenAid%20repair%20specialist%2C%20which%20can%20be%20expensive%2C%20so%20you're%20better%20off%20purchasing%20a%20stand%20mixer%20with%20a%20wattage%20that%20meets%20your%20needs%20from%20the%20get-go.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fkitchenaid-stand-mixer-classic-plus-review%5C%22%3Ereview%20of%20the%20KitchenAid%20Classic%20Plus%20stand%20mixer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20bread%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20KitchenAid%20Pro%20Line%20Series%207-Quart%20Bowl%20Lift%20Stand%20Mixer%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f99d0306f5b310011724000%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStiff%20or%20heavy%20doughs%20like%20bagel%20dough%2C%20pizza%20dough%2C%20and%20some%20noodle%20doughs%20require%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20power%20to%20knead%20properly%2C%20which%20can%20be%20taxing%20on%20many%20stand%20mixers.%20The%C2%A07-Quart%20Pro-Line%20model%C2%A0has%20a%20970%20watt%20motor%20for%20powerful%20and%20thorough%20kneading%20without%20overheating%20the%20mixer.%20The%20wider%20bowl-lift%20design%20also%20provides%20more%20stability%20during%20mixing%2C%20so%20the%20mixer%20doesn't%20%26quot%3Bwalk%26quot%3B%20or%20shake%20as%20much%20during%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20model%20I%20primarily%20used%20during%20a%20decade%20of%20work%20in%20professional%20kitchens.%20The%20machine%20is%20reliable%2C%20nimble%2C%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20and%20remarkably%20quiet%20for%20such%20a%20large%20mixer.%20It%20can%20handle%20everything%20from%20whipping%20two%20egg%20whites%20to%20mixing%20triple%20batches%20of%20cake%20batter.%20KitchenAid%20claims%20the%207-quart%20size%20can%20make%20up%20to%2014%20dozen%20cookies%20in%20a%20single%20batch%2C%20and%20while%20I%20haven't%20ventured%20to%20test%20the%20limits%20of%20that%20claim%20(I%20love%20cookies%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20need%2014%20dozen)%2C%20it%20made%20double%20batches%20of%20compost%20cookies%20and%20bagels%20with%20plenty%20of%20room%20to%20spare.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wide%20bowl%20is%20easy%20to%20remove%20from%20the%20mixer%2C%20has%20a%20large%20comfortable%20handle%2C%20and%20provides%20lots%20of%20space%20for%20adding%20ingredients%20during%20mixing.%20Avid%20bakers%20and%20especially%20those%20who%20make%20bread%20will%20appreciate%20its%20reliability%20%E2%80%94%20these%20mixers%20saw%20heavy%20daily%20use%20when%20I%20worked%20with%20them%20in%20professional%20kitchens%20and%20rarely%20needed%20repairs.%20If%20you%20take%20care%20of%20this%20mixer%2C%20it's%20likely%20to%20last%20you%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20it's%20a%20hefty%20machine%20and%20not%20the%20sort%20of%20mixer%20you%20want%20to%20lug%20around%2C%20so%20it's%20best%20for%20those%20with%20ample%20counter%20space%20to%20devote%20to%20its%20large%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fkitchenaid-pro-line-stand-mixer-review%5C%22%3Efull%20review%20of%20the%20KitchenAid%20Pro%20Line%20stand%20mixer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20small%20spaces%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222995%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20red%20KitchenAid%20mini%20stand%20mixer%20on%20a%20counter%20in%20a%20kitchen%20next%20to%20KitchenAid%20attachments.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e4cb65b698ac0019df2563%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222246%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20into%20a%20600%20square%20foot%20apartment%2C%20every%20inch%20felt%20precious.%20Since%20counter%20space%20was%20limited%2C%20I%20needed%20a%20mixer%20light%20enough%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20mind%20hauling%20it%20out%20from%20a%20cabinet%20every%20time%20I%20wanted%20to%20bake.%20The%20KitchenAid%20Artisan%20Mini%203.5%20Quart%20Tilt-Head%20Stand%20Mixer%C2%A0hit%20all%20these%20marks%20for%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeasuring%20just%20over%2011%20inches%20wide%2C%20the%20Mini%20is%20about%2025%25%20smaller%20than%20our%20best%20overall%20pick.%20While%20this%20may%20not%20seem%20like%20a%20drastic%20difference%2C%20the%20Mini%20is%20much%20more%20maneuverable%2C%20and%20I%20love%20that%20it%20fits%20easily%20under%20my%20cabinets%20or%20on%20a%20shelf.%20Less%20surface%20area%20also%20means%20less%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20the%20Mini's%20work%20bowl%20doesn't%20hog%20space%20in%20my%20sink%20or%20dishwasher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20more%20petite%2C%20the%20Mini%20is%20perfectly%20capable%20of%20whipping%20up%20a%20single%20batch%20of%20cookies%20or%20biscuits.%20I've%20made%20muffins%2C%20pasta%20dough%2C%20bread%20dough%2C%20pizza%20dough%2C%20cake%2C%20frosting%2C%20and%20more%20cookies%20than%20I%20can%20count%20in%20the%20Mini%20with%20no%20issues%20or%20changes%20to%20the%20mixing%20times%20called%20for%20in%20the%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20put%20my%20Mini%20through%20strenuous%20tests%20for%20this%20guide%2C%20it%20showed%20some%20of%20its%20limitations.%20The%20work%20bowl%20was%20%3Cem%3Ejust%3C%2Fem%3E%20able%20to%20fit%20all%20the%20mix-ins%20for%20compost%20cookies%2C%20but%20it%20started%20to%20overflow%20a%20bit%20when%20I%20turned%20on%20the%20mixer.%20Bagel%20dough%20also%20came%20together%20fine%2C%20but%20the%20mixer%20shook%20and%20%26quot%3Bwalked%26quot%3B%20around%20the%20counter%20during%20the%20long%20kneading%20time%2C%20enough%20so%20that%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20it%20for%20the%20whole%2010%20minutes%20it%20was%20mixing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20if%20space%20is%20your%20primary%20concern%20or%20you're%20an%20occasional%20baker%2C%20the%20Mini%20is%20a%20great%20option%20for%20an%20unobtrusive%20machine%20that%20can%20do%20just%20about%20anything%20a%20full-size%20mixer%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fkitchenaid-artisan-mini-stand-mixer-review%5C%22%3Ereview%20of%20the%20KitchenAid%20Mini%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20out%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20each%20stand%20mixer%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20drew%20from%20my%20own%20experience%20as%20a%20food%20editor%20working%20in%20professional%20kitchens%20and%20using%20these%20mixers%20over%20many%20years%2C%20I%20also%20put%20each%20model%20through%20a%20standard%20set%20of%20tests%20to%20see%20how%20they'd%20compare%20to%20each%20other.%20Here's%20how%20I%20evaluated%20KitchenAid%20stand%20mixers%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%2C%20capacity%2C%20and%20ease%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20weighed%20and%20measured%20all%20the%20stand%20mixers%2C%20including%20comparing%20the%20stated%20versus%20functional%20capacity%20(the%20capacity%20when%20measured%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20work%20bowl%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20mixing%20attachment)%20of%20each%20work%20bowl.%20I%20carried%20the%20mixers%20around%20and%20noted%20how%20comfortable%20they%20were%20to%20move%20and%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20consulted%20the%20company%20to%20learn%20the%20power%20of%20each%20motor%20in%20watts.%20Residential%20stand%20mixers%20range%20from%20250%20to%20970%20watts%2C%20and%20mixers%20with%20higher%20wattage%20motors%20can%20mix%20heavy%2C%20wet%20doughs%20more%20readily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhipping%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20whipped%20two%20egg%20whites%20to%20stiff%20peaks%20in%20each%20mixer%2C%20which%20tests%20the%20mixers'%20control%20during%20gradual%20ramping%20up%20of%20speed.%20It%20also%20tested%20the%20larger%20mixers'%20ability%20to%20function%20well%20even%20with%20a%20very%20small%20volume%20of%20ingredients.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreaming%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20used%20each%20stand%20mixer%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_090117_best-kitchenaid-mixers-20%26h%3Dbd7ea01182b49e5a1c6c689f44fc06634c314c32ac75d0639eceb7d59ef18e0c%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f415cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-kitchenaid%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmilkbarstore.com%252Fblogs%252Frecipes%252Fcompost-cookie-new%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMilk%20Bar%20compost%20cookies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20have%20more%20than%205%20cups%20of%20mix-ins.%20Not%20only%20did%20this%20test%20the%20functional%20capacity%20of%20the%20mixers%2C%20but%20also%20their%20ability%20to%20operate%20on%20different%20speeds%20%E2%80%94%20high%20speed%20for%20creaming%20butter%20and%20sugar%2C%20and%20low%20speed%20for%20incorporating%20delicate%20mix-ins%20like%20chips%20and%20pretzels%20without%20breaking%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKneading%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEach%20mixer%20was%20used%20to%20make%20a%20batch%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kingarthurbaking.com%2Frecipes%2Fbagels-recipe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKing%20Arthur%20bagels%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20a%20stiff%20dough%20with%20a%20long%2C%2010%20minute%20mixing%20time.%20I%20made%20a%20note%20if%20any%20of%20the%20mixers%20shook%20or%20walked%2C%20struggled%2C%20or%20made%20excessive%20noise%20during%20this%20tough%20task.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20true%20test%20of%20a%20stand%20mixer%20is%20how%20it%20performs%20over%20time.%20While%20I%20included%20information%20from%20my%20own%20experience%20working%20with%20these%20models%20over%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20I'll%20continue%20to%20use%20the%20stand%20mixers%20in%20this%20guide%20and%20report%20back%20on%20any%20durability%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20to%20choose%20which%20stand%20mixer%20is%20the%20right%20choice%20for%20you%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20burgundy%20red%20KitchenAid%20Stand%20Mixer%20on%20a%20cutting%20board%20in%20a%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f99d5616f5b310011724045%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWattage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20higher%20the%20wattage%20of%20the%20motor%2C%20the%20more%20powerful%20the%20mixer%20will%20be.%20Mixers%20with%20higher%20wattage%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20970%20watt%20motor%20on%20the%20KitchenAid%20Pro%20%E2%80%94%20glide%20through%20tough%20doughs%20and%20don't%20easily%20overheat.%20If%20you%20bake%20at%20least%20once%20a%20week%20or%20you%20regularly%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20heavy%2C%20wet%20doughs%20like%20pizza%20or%20bread%20dough%2C%20then%20you'll%20benefit%20from%20a%20larger%2C%20more%20expensive%20model%20with%20a%20high%20wattage%20motor%20built%20for%20power%20and%20durability.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20who%20breaks%20out%20the%20stand%20mixer%20once%20a%20year%20to%20make%20holiday%20cookies%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20the%20Cadillac%20of%20KitchenAids.%20Occasional%20bakers%20will%20be%20perfectly%20well%20off%20with%20250%20or%20275-watt%20models%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_090117_best-kitchenaid-mixers-20%26h%3Dea1a585cf9dfd0fa945ae8c3eaa9654e67fbd74c0aeae62c3fd587d30a4ca116%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f415cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252F