0but%20it%20also%20wouldn't%20operate%20effectively%20since%20the%20ingredients%20would%20actually%20cover%20the%20mixing%20attachment.%20Instead%2C%20the%20functional%20capacity%20is%20measured%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bowl%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20mixing%20attachment%20and%20it's%20usually%20about%201%20to%201.5%20quarts%20less%20than%20the%20stated%20capacity.%20One%20quart%20is%20about%20the%20size%20of%20a%20large%20deli%20container%2C%20so%20if%20you%20have%20a%20recipe%20that%20regularly%20makes%20enough%20dough%20to%20fill%20four%20or%20five%20of%20those%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20mixer%20with%20a%20larger%20stated%20capacity%20of%206%20or%207%20quarts.%20It's%20also%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20buy%20a%20mixer%20with%20a%20larger%20capacity%20if%20you%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20bread%20since%20the%20mixer%20needs%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20clearance%20to%20knead%20the%20dough%20effectively.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManeuverability%20and%20storage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20bigger%20the%20capacity%20and%20more%20powerful%20the%20mixer%2C%20the%20heavier%20and%20larger%20the%20mixer%20will%20be.%20The%20largest%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20in%20our%20guide%20can%20weigh%20almost%2030%20pounds.%20Unless%20you're%20comfortable%20regularly%20lifting%20an%20appliance%20of%20that%20size%2C%20you'll%20either%20need%20to%20consider%20a%20small%20mixer%20or%20have%20dedicated%20counter%20space.%20Larger%20mixers%20will%20take%20up%20about%20half%20the%20width%20of%20a%20standard%20size%20counter%20and%20may%20not%20fit%20readily%20under%20your%20cabinet%20overhang.%20If%20space%20is%20at%20a%20premium%2C%20consider%20a%20smaller%2C%20less%20expensive%20mixer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%20and%20customization%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20For%20some%20people%2C%20the%20most%20important%20factor%20in%20choosing%20the%20best%20KitchenAid%20is%20the%20color.%20If%20a%20fun%20color%20is%20your%20priority%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20mixer%20from%20KitchenAid's%20Artisan%20series.%20Our%20best%20mixer%20for%20small%20spaces%20and%20best%20overall%20pick%20are%20both%20Artisan%20mixers%20and%20are%20available%20in%20up%20to%2047%20different%20colors.%20Our%20best%20overall%20pick%20also%20offers%20further%20customization%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_090117_best-kitchenaid-mixers-20%26h%3De447eb0f72b27f91fb975d747fdc0d5b5f14e5de1ee27c8de33e30435448044e%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f415cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-kitchenaid%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.kitchenaid.com%252Fcountertop-appliances%252Fstand-mixers%252Fbowls.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterchangeable%20decorative%20work%20bowls%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20various%20patterns%20and%20materials.%20The%20Classic%20and%20Pro%20Line%20series%20offer%20a%20much%20more%20limited%20color%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20just%20red%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20neutrals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShould%20I%20buy%20a%20KitchenAid%20stand%20mixer%3F%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20other%20stand%20mixer%20brands%20out%20there%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Breville%2C%20Sunbeam%2C%20Oster%2C%20and%20Bosch%20%E2%80%94%20none%20are%20as%20ubiquitous%20or%20revered%20as%20the%20KitchenAid%20stand%20mixer.%20Some%20people%20consider%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yahoo.com%2Flifestyle%2Fis-getting-your-own-stand-mixer-the-new-life-milestone-85835918236.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurchasing%20the%20best%20KitchenAid%20stand%20mixer%20to%20be%20a%20life%20milestone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theknotww.com%2Fpress-releases%2F9918%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Knot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20KitchenAid%20stand%20mixer%20was%20the%20most-wished-for%20product%20on%20wedding%20registries%20in%202021.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smithsonianmag.com%2Fsmithsonian-institution%2F100-years-kitchenaid-has-been-stand-brand-stand-mixers-180972838%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DJulia%2520Child%2520eventually%2520fell%2520in%2Cto%2520the%2520Smithsonian%2520in%25202001.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJulia%20Child's%20KitchenAid%20mixer%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20lives%20in%20the%20Smithsonian%20Museum.%20But%20what%20makes%20the%20best%20KitchenAid%20stand%20mixers%20so%20special%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKitchenAid%20stand%20mixers%20have%20been%20around%20for%20more%20than%20a%20century.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_090117_best-kitchenaid-mixers-20%26h%3D68465b0cb43fbaa6c6714c8c5195b1523f45598070be705a97e04062bb3d5696%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f415cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-kitchenaid%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.kitchenaid.com%252F100year%252Fhistory.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20KitchenAid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20brand%20got%20its%20name%20in%201919%20when%20an%20executive's%20wife%20called%20the%20first%20home%20model%20stand%20mixer%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20kitchen%20aid%20I've%20ever%20had.%26quot%3B%20The%20name%20stuck%20and%20KitchenAid%20has%20been%20synonymous%20with%20stand%20mixers%20ever%20since.%20While%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20great%20stand%20mixers%20from%20other%20brands%20out%20there%2C%20KitchenAid%20still%20stands%20out%20in%20a%20number%20of%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I've%20tried%20almost%20every%20brand%20of%20stand%20mixer%20out%20there%20in%20my%20seven%20years%20reviewing%20kitchen%20products%2C%20and%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20that%20use%20an%20almost%20all-metal%20construction.%20Other%20brands%20cut%20costs%20by%20using%20plastic%20in%20part%20of%20the%20design%3A%20either%20in%20the%20body%20of%20the%20mixer%2C%20on%20knobs%20and%20dials%2C%20in%20the%20mixing%20attachments%2C%20or%20even%20in%20the%20gears.%20Mixers%20made%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20plastic%20are%20usually%20lighter%20and%20less%20expensive%2C%20but%20much%20less%20durable.%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20can%20last%20for%20decades%20because%20of%20their%20strong%20metal%20parts.%20While%20this%20stronger%20construction%20comes%20at%20a%20premium%20%E2%80%94%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20are%20among%20the%20most%20expensive%20out%20there%20%E2%80%94%20their%20durability%20makes%20them%20a%20great%20investment.%20Even%20the%20most%20affordable%20KitchenAid%20mixer%20shares%20this%20same%20hearty%20construction%20and%20powerful%20motor%20and%20will%20last%20for%20decades%20with%20proper%20care.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20robust%20network%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fproducthelp.kitchenaid.com%2FCountertop_Appliances%2FStand_Mixers%2FProduct_Info%2FStand_Mixer_Cleaning_and_Care%2FStand_Mixer_Repair_Options%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthorized%20KitchenAid%20repair%20technicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20can%20repair%20your%20stand%20mixer%20if%20something%20does%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20all-metal%20design%20makes%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20much%20heavier%20than%20most%20other%20brands.%20While%20they%20can%20be%20a%20pain%20to%20lug%20around%2C%20the%20added%20heft%20produces%20an%20important%20benefit%3A%20more%20stability%20when%20mixing.%20Lighter%20machines%20can%20shake%20or%20%26quot%3Bwalk%26quot%3B%20off%20countertops.%20The%20heaviness%20of%20KitchenAid%20mixers%20helps%20them%20stay%20put.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20mixer%20for%20everybody%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Many%20brands%20that%20make%20stand%20mixers%20only%20produce%20one%20or%20two%20models.%20KitchenAid%20makes%20almost%20a%20dozen%20models%20with%20diff