r%20vindication%20than%20this%20of%20our%20secular%20policies%2C%20our%20Constitution%2C%20that%20we%20have%20drawn%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20towards%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20just%20imagine%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarked%20with%20apprehension%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20would%20have%20happened%20in%20Kashmir%20if%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%20or%20any%20other%20communal%20party%20had%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20apprehensions%20fructified%20by%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20far-sighted%20observation%20of%20Kashmir%20chillingly%20played%20out%20when%20in%20August%202019%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20successor%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%E2%80%9D%20and%20its%20leader%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20with%20a%20huge%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20controlled%20the%20entire%20state%20apparatus%20and%20unilaterally%20downgraded%20J%26amp%3BK%20from%20a%20full-fledged%20state%20to%20a%20Union%20territory%20(UT)%20while%20also%20doing%20away%20with%20its%20special%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20suffered%20from%20a%20huge%20democratic%20deficit%20for%20no%20fault%20of%20their%20own%20and%20confronted%20several%20harsh%20measures%2C%20including%20prolonged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-4g-internet-costs%5C%22%3EInternet%3C%2Fa%3E%20bans%20and%20a%20clampdown%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-delimitation-over-2-voter-revisions-done-but-elections-nowhere-in-sight%5C%22%3Eelectoral%20processes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20without%20which%20they%20remained%20unrepresented%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20their%C2%A0government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fends-matter-not-the-means-decoding-scs-approval-for-reading-down-of-article-370%5C%22%3EEnds%20Matter%2C%20Not%20the%20Means%3A%20Decoding%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Approval%20for%20Reading%20Down%20of%20Article%20370%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENehru%20linked%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20issue%20with%20Kashmir%20in%201950%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20quite%20coincidental%20that%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20December%2022-23%2C%201949%2C%20two%20idols%20%E2%80%93%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Sita%20%E2%80%93%20were%20surreptitiously%20placed%20under%20the%20central%20dome%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Nehru%20expressed%20his%20anxiety%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20United%20Provinces%20(now%20Uttar%20Pradesh)%20that%20this%20development%C2%A0could%20affect%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20letter%20he%20wrote%20on%20February%205%2C%201950%2C%20to%20G.B.%20Pant%2C%20Nehru%20categorically%20stated%20that%20the%20developments%20concerning%20the%20idols%E2%80%99%20secret%20placement%20would%20spell%20serious%20consequences%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20and%20gravely%20impact%20the%20Kashmir%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20reproduce%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20exact%20words%20from%20that%20letter.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20shall%20be%20glad%20if%20you%20will%20keep%20me%20informed%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20situation.%20As%20you%20know%2C%20I%20attached%20great%20importance%20to%20it%20and%20to%20its%20repercussions%20on%20all-India%20affairs%20and%20more%20especially%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20remarks%20by%20Nehru%20brought%20out%20his%20sensitivity%20in%20understanding%2C%20in%201950%20itself%2C%20that%20the%20placement%20of%20those%20idols%20inside%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20would%20exacerbate%20communal%20problems%20so%20severely%20that%20the%20secular%20fabric%20of%20our%20country%20would%20be%20torn%20apart%2C%20and%20the%20democratic%20processes%20set%20in%20motion%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20after%20it%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Union%20would%20be%20badly%20vitiated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fears%20expressed%20by%20Nehru%20about%20Jana%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20unfavourable%20disposal%20towards%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20been%20materialised%20by%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20regime.%20Apart%20from%20scrapping%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20in%C2%A0August%202019%20and%20downgrading%20it%20to%20a%20UT%2C%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-ram-temple-ayodhya-foundation-stone%5C%22%3Elaid%20the%20foundation%20brick%20for%20a%20Ram%20temple%3C%2Fa%3E%20almost%20exactly%20a%20year%20later%20at%20the%20same%20place%20where%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20was%20illegally%20demolished%2C%20following%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20permitting%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fayodhyatimeline%5C%22%3EAyodhya%3A%20Once%20There%20Was%20a%20Mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20remarkable%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20the%20land%20to%20those%20who%20demolished%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20Ram%20temple%20in%20the%20same%20place%20where%20that%20mosque%20once%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20apex%20court%2C%20in%20another%20remarkable%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-kashmir-article-370-verdict%5C%22%3Eapproved%20the%20abrogation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20evaded%20adjudicating%20the%20issue%20of%20its%20reduction%20to%20a%20UT%20even%20as%20it%20upheld%20the%20UT%20status%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20one%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20erstwhile%20constituent%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20status%20was%20downgraded%20to%20a%20UT%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20while%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20was%20imposed%20%E2%80%93%20because%20the%20politically%20appointed%20governor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fplan-for-grand-coalition-in-jk-prompts-governor-to-dissolve-assembly%5C%22%3Edissolved%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state%20assembly%20in%20November%202018.%20This%20raises%20the%20concern%20that%20what%20was%20done%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20can%20be%20done%20to%20any%20other%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prospect%20is%20worrisome%20as%20far%20as%20federalism%20is%20concerned.%20The%20overwhelming%20sway%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20tinkering%20with%20the%20statehood%20of%20a%20federal%20unit%20has%20grave%20implications%20for%20the%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20192340%2FH20220424111143.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20192340%2FH20220424111143.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20192340%2FH20220424111143-300x154.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20192340%2FH20220424111143-1024x525.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-641296%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22615%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20LG%20Manoj%20Sinha%20at%20an%20exhibition%20in%20Samba%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20April%2024%2C%202022.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemocratic%20deficit%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20assembly%20was%20dissolved%20in%20November%202018%2C%20elections%20have%20so%20far%20not%20been%20conducted%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20It%20has%20troubled%20all%20those%20who%20believed%20in%20our%20constitutional%20scheme%20of%20governance%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20which%20is%20a%20federal%20framework%20and%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20upholding%20the%20revocation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370%2C%20even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fpdf%2FLU%2Farticle_370.pdf%5C%22%3Eelections%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20assembly%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20be%20completed%20before%20September%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20India%20has%20any%20Union%20government%20downgraded%20a%20state%20to%20a%20UT%20as%20was%20unilaterally%20done%20in%20the%20case%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20has%20serious%20implications%20for%20its%20identity%20and%20democratic%20credentials%20as%20an%20organic%20component%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-ladakh-union-territory%5C%22%3EHistorically%2C%20UTs%20Become%20States.%20Now%20the%20Centre%20Is%20Reversing%20That%20Trend%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20note%20that%20even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20accession%20to%20the%20Indian%20Union%20in%20October%201947%20in%20the%20face%20of%20an%20invasion%C2%A0by%20Pakistan-backed%20Pashtun%20tribesmen%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20making%20it%20a%20part%20of%20that%20country%2C%20Nehru%20never%20contemplated%20making%20it%20a%20UT%20and%20ensuring%20direct%20rule%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20it%20is%20rather%20shocking%20that%20those%20who%20vociferously%20claimed%20that%20the%20abrogation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20status%20would%20end%20all%20forms%20of%20terrorism%20there%20and%20bring%20it%20all-round%20progress%20have%20failed%20to%20restore%20its%20statehood%20even%20four%20years%20after%20it%20was%20downgraded%20to%20a%20UT%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20ensure%20elections%20and%20the%20large-scale%20participation%20of%20its%20people%20in%20its%20representative%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20even%20MPs%20and%20several%20others%20%E2%80%93%20be%20they%20journalists%20or%20civil%20society%20representatives%20%E2%80%93%20who%20took%20a%20critical%20stand%20against%20direct%20rule%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20were%20subjected%20to%20coercive%20measures%2C%20incarceration%20and%20prolonged%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long-drawn-out%20internet%20clampdown%20in%20the%20whole%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20very%20gravely%20impaired%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20rights%20and%20liberties%20to%20communicate.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fright-to-access-to-internet-a-fundamental-right-sc-on-jk-restrictions-6209407%2F%5C%22%3Einterpreted%20the%20right%20to%20access%20the%20internet%20as%20a%20fundamental%20right%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20so%20in%20shutting%20it%20down%2C%20the%20regime%20there%20grossly%20infringed%20upon%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20its%20accession%20to%20the%20Indian%20Union%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20never%20suffered%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20deprivation%20of%20their%20democratic%20rights%2C%20which%20were%20affirmed%20by%20establishing%20a%20representative%20government%20in%20place%20of%20its%20monarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20telling%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20conduct%20elections%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20state%20assembly.%20It%20represents%20a%20sorry%20state%20of%20affairs%20that%20Nehru%20apprehended%20J%26amp%3BK%20would%20be%20reduced%20to%20in%20case%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%20controlled%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERid%20India%20of%20the%20communal%20virus%20by%20learning%20from%20Kashmir%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20a%20statement%20in%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20(legislative)%20on%20March%205%2C%201948%2C%20Nehru%20categorically%20stated%20that%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20issue%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20of%20communalism%2C%20and%20that%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20should%20learn%20from%20it%20the%20lessons%20of%20communal%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20India%2C%20currently%20embroiled%20in%20a%20majoritarian%20narrative%2C%20save%20itself%20from%20a%20communal%20imbroglio%20by%20defending%20the%20secular%20and%20composite%20ethos%20of%20Kashmir%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fs-n-sahu%5C%22%3ES.N.%20Sahu%3C%2Fa%3E%20served%20as%20an%20officer%20on%20special%20duty%20to%20President%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702484131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FNehru.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnehru-prescient-apprehensions-jana-sangh-kashmir-bjp-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nehru%20wondered%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%20party%E2%80%9D%20such%20as%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20Kashmir.%20Cut%20to%20the%20present%2C%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20under%20a%20clampdown%20on%20rights%20and%20democracy%20imposed%20by%20the%20Jana%20Sangh's%20successor%2C%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnehru-prescient-apprehensions-jana-sangh-kashmir-bjp-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Western%20Section%20of%20China-India%20Border%20Belongs%20to%20China'%3A%20Beijing%20on%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Article%20370%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F31211511%2FW020230531715249452708final.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20China%20addressed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20order%20upholding%20the%20dilution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20autonomy%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20day%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20verdict%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20change%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20western%20section%20of%20the%20China-India%20border%20has%20always%20belonged%20to%20China%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20said%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fafter-supreme-court-order-china-reiterates-position-on-kashmir%5C%22%3Econsistent%20and%20clear-cut%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20resolved%20peacefully%20and%20appropriately%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20UN%20Charter%2C%20Security%20Council%20resolutions%20and%20relevant%20bilateral%20agreement%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0but%20did%20not%20explicitly%20refer%20to%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20she%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20union%20territory%20of%20Ladakh%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fmfa_eng%2Fxwfw_665399%2Fs2510_665401%2F202312%2Ft20231213_11201747.html%5C%22%3Edaily%20briefing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20which%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CChina%20has%20never%20recognised%20the%20so-called%20union%20territory%20of%20Ladakh%20set%20up%20unilaterally%20and%20illegally%20by%20India.%20India%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20judicial%20verdict%20does%20not%20change%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20western%20section%20of%20the%20China-India%20border%20has%20always%20belonged%20to%20China.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20India%20signed%20the%20Shimla%20agreement%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20refused%20to%20accept%20any%20third-party%E2%80%9