20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJeremy%20Hunt%20and%20his%20family.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40Jeremy_Hunt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20well%20be%20that%20these%20marriages%20would%20have%20been%20unaffected%20even%20if%20the%20higher%20earnings%20threshold%20was%20in%20place%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%93%20but%20surely%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20can%20empathise%20with%20youngsters%20who%20fall%20in%20love%20across%20national%20boundaries%2C%20and%20can%20seek%20to%20enable%20rather%20than%20impede%20international%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20intention%20is%20to%20look%20tough%20on%20immigration%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20general%20election.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20clamping%20down%20on%20entry%20for%20dependants%20of%20overseas%20students.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20tightening%20restrictions%20on%20work%20visas%20for%20all%20except%20high%20earners%20and%20those%20with%20skills%2C%20such%20as%20in%20health%20or%20social%20care%2C%20which%20are%20in%20great%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENet%20legal%20immigration%20to%20Britain%20is%20currently%20running%20at%20750%2C000%20a%20year%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20more%20than%201%25%20of%20the%20current%20population.%20The%20figure%20is%20consistently%20rising%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20ministers%20are%20pledging%20to%20bring%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20contested%20aspect%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20new%20immigration%20policy%20concerns%20the%20much%20smaller%20number%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20%E2%80%93%20about%2030%2C000%20a%20year%20%E2%80%93%20who%20travel%20across%20the%20Channel%20on%20unseaworthy%20and%20overcrowded%20small%20boats.%20Sunak%20is%20persisting%20with%20his%20plans%20to%20deport%20asylum%20seekers%20to%20Rwanda%20in%20central%20Africa%2C%20even%20though%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20introducing%20legislation%20which%20will%20sidestep%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20by%20declaring%20Rwanda%20a%20safe%20destination%20for%20refugees%20%E2%80%93%20as%20if%20Parliament%20voting%20that%20the%20moon%20is%20made%20of%20cheese%20means%20that%20it%20really%20is.%20One%20wing%20of%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20views%20this%20as%20outrageously%20illiberal%3B%20another%20is%20complaining%20loudly%20that%20the%20government%20must%20go%20further%20and%20override%20the%20European%20Convention%20on%20Human%20Rights.%20The%20issue%20could%20precipitate%20a%20government%20defeat%20in%20Parliament%20which%20in%20turn%20may%20bring%20forward%20the%20next%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20the%20advice%20has%20to%20be%3A%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20thinking%20of%20marrying%20a%20Brit%2C%20beware!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Ffrino%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Whitehead%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20honorary%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nottingham%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20a%20former%20BBC%20India%20Correspondent.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702463408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13131513%2Fdownload-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdont-marry-a-brit-unless-theyre-really-rich%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20measure%20to%20limit%20immigration%2C%20the%20British%20government%20announced%20that%20the%20minimum%20income%20required%20to%20bring%20a%20foreign%20spouse%20into%20the%20country%20on%20a%20family%20visa%20will%20rise%20sharply.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdont-marry-a-brit-unless-theyre-really-rich%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Security%20breach%20inside%20India's%20parliament%20building%20with%20canisters%20of%20'foul-smelling'%20smoke%20set%20off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22