%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaster%20the%20easier%20surgery%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20says%20that%20there%20are%20several%20types%20of%20surgical%20procedures%20in%20pearl%20cultures%20%E2%80%94%20like%20gonadal%20implantation%2C%20mantle%20tissue%20implantation%2C%20and%20mantle%20cavity%20insertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20suggest%20that%20farmers%20learn%20mantle%20tissue%20surgery%20as%20it%20is%20easier%20to%20perform%20and%20the%20chances%20of%20oysters%20are%20higher%20as%20compared%20to%20other%20kinds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%20the%20pond%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20informs%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20provide%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267186%2Fpearl-farming-cultivation-oyster-shell-home-made-pond-set-up-ashok-manwani-kuljana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eriver-like%20ecosystem%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20oysters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COysters%20should%20not%20feel%20alienated%20and%20that%20they%20are%20outside%20a%20river.%20They%20must%20have%20a%20river-like%20environment%20to%20thrive.%20To%20ensure%20this%2C%20you%20must%20introduce%20algae%20inside%20the%20pond.%20Algae%20is%20the%20major%20food%20source%20of%20an%20oyster%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20the%20pH%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20points%20out%20that%20farmers%20should%20ensure%20a%20pH%20of%20eight%20inside%20the%20water%20tank.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20pH%20is%20more%20than%20eight%20(alkaline)%2C%20oysters%20will%20not%20survive.%20You%20should%20also%20check%20pH%20levels%20weekly.%20If%20the%20pH%20is%20higher%2C%20keep%20changing%20the%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20a%2020%C3%9720%20square%20feet%20pond%20with%2010%20feet%20depth%2C%20it%20would%20have%20the